messages.content: Show me all Bayern Munich Bundesliga matches in a year of your choice. Give the date and time of each match, and the result
I do not have access to a database of football matches. I can show you the stadiums of Bayern Munich and some of their opponents in the 2019-2020 Bundesliga season.

Okay, I've added the home stadiums for all 18 Bundesliga teams from the 2019-2020 season to the map. You can click on any of the stadium icons to see the name of the stadium and the home team that plays there. The map is now centered over Germany to give you a nice overview of where all the clubs are located.
Give a timeline of the matches played by Bayern.

I am sorry, but I do not have access to the specific dates or results of the matches. I can show you the locations of the stadiums for all the teams in the 2019-2020 Bundesliga season, which are already on the map.

I understand your frustration. My capabilities are focused on geography and history, and I don't have access to specific sports statistics like match timelines and scores. I apologize that I couldn't help with your original request.

However, I can offer a different perspective on the season. How about I show you the routes for some of Bayern Munich's away games? This will give you a sense of the travel and logistics involved in a Bundesliga season. For example, I can draw the route from their home stadium in Munich to their biggest rival's stadium in Dortmund. Would you be interested in something like that?
